{"tid":317670,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"西藏旅程","createTime":"2017-07-11T15:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T18:59:56.000Z","uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"054757fa2c5603a28326ff1b742d11dc69a7d690","tid":317670,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:05:16.000Z","msg":"我同另外3個fd打算8月中去西藏，岩岩上網查左資料，原本好似去其他地方咁，book死一間酒店，再自已包車周圍去，但發現有時侯有d景點可以係山上過夜咁<br />\n<br />\n所以想請教各位巴打，去西藏係搵d 公司報名自組4人團或加埋其他人，定係自己book間酒店包車自己周圍去咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我叫有d公司有埋路線，包車，又包不同景點既酒店，所以想問下有經驗既巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a69db7f86d2659a93f0457a40dc6bea810012cd","tid":317670,"uid":43757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:20:52.000Z","msg":"你玩咩線?"},{"pid":"7205c6faa42359d2655c120c690a48d1e7a0377b","tid":317670,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你玩咩線?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見每個景點都好耐車程，睇完d名完全冇概念係邊到打邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0b004ee21e71653ac44fa5d77561ad4c83bda1","tid":317670,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"岩岩我查左，係話買張火車飛去到西藏，跟個司機玩，佢會plan好晒，巴打有冇司機介紹？我見背包客棧都有，但唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03991686b267623657984e1e508d6a677580ee87","tid":317670,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"就算你納木錯唔過夜<br />\n<br />\n林芝線同珠峰線都要過夜 2-3晚"},{"pid":"b636e87cafe182e1414248fd626b054d0e2c9618","tid":317670,"uid":1391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"我建議係你睇清楚想去邊d景點同預幾多日先再同司機傾"},{"pid":"9256792efb732978b432a32d1b7aaec52ef2b250","tid":317670,"uid":43757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"通常分幾條線，<br />\n<br />\n阿里南線<br />\n阿里大北線<br />\n青藏線<br />\n川藏線<br />\n<br />\n你上網睇下有乜心水。<br />\n羊湖珠峰呢啲就咩線都會去。"},{"pid":"511f244401af7632f76b36d9d4e849b4374ec1b0","tid":317670,"uid":43757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:54:10.000Z","msg":"同埋八月係雨季，<br />\n川藏會山泥傾瀉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議你向西玩阿里"},{"pid":"9274584bac1e6bf2038e1a24f58c42f0290496b3","tid":317670,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩問左價，阿里線12日，4人包車就24000人仔，加埋其他住食，約15000人仔一個，想問下巴打呢個價公唔公道？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2395def5d1a5a1d12e2b388161cc3bbaabcdbb1","tid":317670,"uid":98186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"學野"},{"pid":"8e1c5347127487c55a51ecceb205d7f9cbc27380","tid":317670,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋八月係雨季，<br />\n川藏會山泥傾瀉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議你向西玩阿里</blockquote><br />\nx2<br />\n好大機會路都冇埋"},{"pid":"d7345789db8f818396638d78fd73584f5beb9738","tid":317670,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋八月係雨季，<br />\n川藏會山泥傾瀉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議你向西玩阿里</blockquote><br />\nx2<br />\n好大機會路都冇埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係confirm 左玩阿里線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c34b5300c3ee5de6993d85415d1bd4b43024fea","tid":317670,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-